          <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 0.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-default); padding-bottom: 0.5em;">
            Use License
          </h2>
          <p style="line-height: 1.75; margin: 1.25em 0;">
            Permission is granted to temporarily download one copy of the materials (information or software) on ry-ops's website for personal, non-commercial transitory viewing only. This is the grant of a license, not a transfer of title, and under this license you may not:
          </p>
          <ul style="margin: 1.5em 0; padding-left: 1.5em;">
            <li style="margin: 0.5em 0;">Modify or copy the materials</li>
            <li style="margin: 0.5em 0;">Use the materials for any commercial purpose or for any public display (commercial or non-commercial)</li>
            <li style="margin: 0.5em 0;">Attempt to decompile or reverse engineer any software contained on ry-ops's website</li>
            <li style="margin: 0.5em 0;">Remove any copyright or other proprietary notations from the materials</li>
            <li style="margin: 0.5em 0;">Transfer the materials to another person or "mirror" the materials on any other server</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 0.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-default); padding-bottom: 0.5em;">
            Open Source Projects
          </h2>
          <p style="line-height: 1.75; margin: 1.25em 0;">
            The open source projects featured on this site are subject to their own respective licenses. Please refer to each project's GitHub repository for specific license information. The terms above do not supersede the licensing terms of individual open source projects.
          </p>

          <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 0.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-default); padding-bottom: 0.5em;">
            Disclaimer
          </h2>
          <p style="line-height: 1.75; margin: 1.25em 0;">
            The materials on ry-ops's website are provided on an 'as is' basis. ry-ops makes no warranties, expressed or implied, and hereby disclaims and negates all other warranties including, without limitation, implied warranties or conditions of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement of intellectual property or other violation of rights.
          </p>

          <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 0.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-default); padding-bottom: 0.5em;">
            Limitations
          </h2>
          <p style="line-height: 1.75; margin: 1.25em 0;">
            In no event shall ry-ops or its suppliers be liable for any damages (including, without limitation, damages for loss of data or profit, or due to business interruption) arising out of the use or inability to use the materials on ry-ops's website, even if ry-ops or a ry-ops authorized representative has been notified orally or in writing of the possibility of such damage.
          </p>

          <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 0.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-default); padding-bottom: 0.5em;">
            Links
          </h2>
          <p style="line-height: 1.75; margin: 1.25em 0;">
            ry-ops has not reviewed all of the sites linked to its website and is not responsible for the contents of any such linked site. The inclusion of any link does not imply endorsement by ry-ops of the site. Use of any such linked website is at the user's own risk.
