          <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 0.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-default); padding-bottom: 0.5em;">
            Modifications
          </h2>
          <p style="line-height: 1.75; margin: 1.25em 0;">
            ry-ops may revise these terms of service for its website at any time without notice. By using this website you are agreeing to be bound by the then current version of these terms of service.
          </p>

          <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 0.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-default); padding-bottom: 0.5em;">
            Contact Information
          </h2>
          <p style="line-height: 1.75; margin: 1.25em 0;">
            If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us through <a href="https://github.com/ry-ops" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--text-link); text-decoration: none;">GitHub</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
